title: No. 7 Spartans use blunder to shock No. 12 Michigan, 27-23
text:
> Top News No. 7 Spartans use blunder to shock No. 12 Michigan, 27-23 Michigan State tight end Paul Lang (83) holds up the Paul Bunyan trophy after defeating Michigan 27-23 in an NCAA college football game, Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in Ann Arbor, Mich. The trophy goes to the winner of the game between the two schools. (AP Photo/Carlos Osorio)
